[9.44107, "o", "\r\n  wrote\r\n             \u2713 .mcp.json (registration \u2014 the tools exist)\r\n             \u2713 CLAUDE.md (steering \u2014 the tools get used)\r\n             \u2713 grove.lock (6 grammars)\r\n\r\n  ready      your agent now has grove's tools across its loop:\r\n             outline \u00b7 symbols \u00b7 source \u00b7 callers \u00b7 definition \u00b7 check\r\n\r\n  try it     start a fresh Claude Code session here and ask a\r\n             \"where/what/who-calls\" question \u2014 it routes through grove.\r\n"]
